{"tid":355730,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"印10歲女因姦成孕　法庭﹕年紀太小禁墮胎","createTime":"2017-08-11T13:53:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T03:36:07.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b3cad701e6c42abfa519928fab9625184e9bc84e","tid":355730,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T13:53:46.000Z","msg":"2017年7月22日 星期六<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170722/s00005/1c0eee3f0f15ff1e933a227c207d61fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170722%2Fs00005%2F1c0eee3f0f15ff1e933a227c207d61fc.jpg&h=1c176865&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印度一名10歲女童被舅舅強姦後懷孕，現時胎兒已6個月大，但女童年紀太小，法院徵詢醫療專家意見後，裁定她不能墮胎。<br />\n<br />\n該名女孩感到胃痛，於是告訴父母，才揭發她曾遭舅舅強姦6次，疑犯被捕。女孩家人其後向當地地區法院申請批准女兒墮胎。<br />\n法庭詢問過8名醫療專家意見後，裁定女童現階段不能墮胎。醫療專家指，由於女孩年紀太小不適合停止懷孕，但胎兒已6個月大，懷孕過程容易引起併發症，分娩也會對母嬰構成危險，甚至剖腹產也有重大風險。專家又指，即使能順利誕下嬰兒，他出世後亦可能有危及生命的併發症，包括貧血和高血壓等。<br />\n根據印度法例，女性懷孕20周以上就不能墮胎，除非證明胎兒會危害母親性命或有遺傳問題。<br />\n（獨立報、每日郵報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170722/s00005/1500706500539\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170722%2Fs00005%2F1500706500539&d=BwQPflbAXA7%2Fxo7TH%2BUz79U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=734d217e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170722%2Fs00005%2F1500706500539&h=b444991a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170722/s00005/1500706500539</a>"},{"pid":"21e98bb6a50274e82ba09111f92b3d0d706bf1ea","tid":355730,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T14:00:54.000Z","msg":"痴線，個人個骨架都未生好，真係會陀到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c9f713da28e8bf4aecbefa5eef5227657410ac","tid":355730,"uid":101804,"like":1,"dislike":25,"score":-24,"citedBy":0,"replyTim